
Create a New Repo
=================

Server Side
-----------

# su -s /bin/bash - git
$ mkdir my-repo.git
$ pushd my-repo.git
$ git init --bare
$ popd

Client Side
-----------

$ cd my-repo
$ git init
$ git add .
$ git commit --allow-empty -m 'Initial commit'
$ git remote add origin ssh://git@git.onddo.com<%= @base_path %>/my-repo.git
$ git push origin master

